#: templates/admin/tabs.php:90
msgid "Just to clarify what's going on behind the progress bar in case the dredded 'white screen' appears or a a 500 Internal Server Error is returned:"
msgstr ""

#: templates/admin/tabs.php:92
msgid "First we enter a loop that checks if any records for the selected dataset exist"
msgstr ""

#: templates/admin/tabs.php:93
msgid "Then we ask WordPress (via WP_Query) for a list of 100 ID's from the selected dataset (e.g. 100 Product ID's/Product Category ID's/Order ID's, etc.)"
